```plantuml
@startuml kryptokrauts_ae-prediction-cards

actor User

participant "Frontend (React)" as Frontend
participant "WalletClient" as WalletClient
participant "PredictionCards API" as API
participant "Aeternity Blockchain" as Blockchain
participant "Oracle Service" as OracleService
participant "Process Prediction Service" as ProcessService

User -> Frontend : Interact with UI
Frontend -> WalletClient : Connect to Aeternity Wallet
WalletClient -> API : Call smart contract
API -> Blockchain : Execute prediction functions
Blockchain -> OracleService : Query asset prices
OracleService -> Blockchain : Return price data
Blockchain -> ProcessService : Notify prediction result
ProcessService -> Blockchain : Process outcomes
Blockchain -> API : Update NFT statuses
API -> WalletClient : Return updated NFT data
WalletClient -> Frontend : Display to user

@enduml
```